                                "stop": 7.739,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 59705,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 87-168, Frisby against Schultz will be announced by Justice O\u2019Connor."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 7.739,
                        "stop": 154.85,
